# Geldium Credit Card Delinquency Prediction

AI-powered collections optimization system using XGBoost to predict credit card delinquency risk and enable proactive customer intervention.

**Project completed as part of Commonwealth Bank Gen AI Job Simulation via Forage**

---

## ğŸ“‹ Project Overview

This project develops a machine learning system to predict which credit card customers are at high risk of becoming delinquent (30+ days late on payments). The solution enables Geldium Financial Services to:
- Identify high-risk customers before delinquency occurs
- Prioritize Collections team outreach efforts
- Implement early intervention strategies
- Reduce delinquency rates by 15-20% while maintaining fairness

**Key Achievement:** Built XGBoost model achieving 82% AUC-ROC with comprehensive fairness testing and explainability features.

