This project prioritizes responsible AI practices:

âœ… **Fairness:** Quarterly audits ensure equitable treatment across demographics  
âœ… **Transparency:** SHAP explanations for every prediction  
âœ… **Compliance:** Adheres to ECOA (Fair Lending) and FCRA regulations  
âœ… **Privacy:** No personally identifiable information (PII) in model  
âœ… **Human Oversight:** HIGH RISK decisions require agent review  

